<body>
    <header class="header">
        <h1 class="logo"><a href="/">wpset.org</a>/privacy/</h1>
        <button class="mode" id="switch-theme">Switch theme</button>
    </header>

    <section class="section">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

        <p>
            We value your privacy and are committed to protecting it. This privacy policy outlines how we handle your information when you visit our website.
        </p>

        <article class="article">
            <h3>Information We Collect</h3>
            <p>
                We do not collect any personal information from our users.<br>
                The only data we store is anonymized information that cannot be traced back to any individual.
            </p>
        </article>

        <article class="article">
            <h3>Use of Cookies</h3>
            <p>We use cookies solely for authentication purposes. These cookies are HTTP-only and are not shared with any third parties. They are used to ensure that you remain logged in securely while using our website.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="article">
            <h3>Data Storage</h3>
            <p>All information stored on our servers is anonymized. We ensure that no personally identifiable information is kept or processed.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="article">
            <h3>Third-party Services</h3>
            <p>We do not share any information with third-party services. Your data remains secure and private within our systems.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="article">
            <h3>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h3>
            <p>We may update our privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="article">
            <h3>Contact Us</h3>
            <p>
                Thank you for trusting wpset.org. Your privacy is our priority.<br>
                If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy, please <a href="/contact/">contact us</a>.
            </p>
        </article>
    </section>

    <%- include(views + '/parts/footer') %>
